Today I lost a huge piece of my heart💔My mother, my best friend, the most cherished person that loved me unconditionally the moment she laid eyes on me for the very first time. She kept me safe in her womb, taught me how to love, laugh and have empathy. She was the first person on my favorites list on my phone. Whenever you see a call from (MOM) or (Dad) always answer it because one day that call will never happen again. I love you more than anything my beautiful mother. I will miss you everyday until that special time that we can once again hold eachother.
